The mandala bedding sets are made of incredible quality materials that will provide you with a full & relaxed dream filled with warmth. Description: Each sign is handmade from solid Pine wood We use Chalk paint on all of our lettering to get that vintage/farm look. We use a high quality oil based stain for our s. We use a Flat ultra white interior paint for the white background on all of our boards.Our signs are NOT made with vinyl lettering, & we DO NOT use canvas or thin material for the construction of our products. Our signs are not made by mass production, when you order a sign & it is made JUST FOR YOU. Every sign is hand painted & hand made for each individual order. Each sign will significantly resemble one another, while having its own characteristic due to the knots, wood grain & slight variations of each piece of hand cut wood. We do not try to cover up, change, or get rid of any of these characteristics, we feel this is what makes the sign unique. We lightly distress the s to add to the rustic/ farm look & will include small imperfections which adds to the rustic character of your sign. Our items are made from cut pine, & put together with wood glue & high quality nails. When ordering signs, please be aware that the size could be 1'' larger or smaller. So if you order a 50'' sign, it could be slightly longer 51" or an inch shorter 49". This happens during the inspection of our boards, we do this in the interest of our customers to ensure your getting a clean, gorgeous piece of wood. (Due to knots & imperfections) These signs are made to be used indoors, but can be placed outdoors although they will age, fade & may warp outdoors. Name: Antique Copper Bed Warmer Or Warming Pan 38 " Star On Lid
Description: This is a Antique Copper Bed Warmer or Warming Pan with a Star design on the Lid. It measures approx. 38 inches long. The handle is wood & it has been turned. There is a hole in the end of the wood handle where a little metal loop used to be so it could be hung on the wall, but it is missing. These were made from the 1500's to the late 1800's. Guess they finally figured out the putting embers in them to warm a bed up was not so safe to breathe & also caused fires. Glad we do not have to use them anymore. It is in good condition with normal age wear. I will let the buyer clean it if they want to shine the copper up...I do not like to alter antiques & collectibles. This would really look great hanging by a Fireplace for the Farm look. I ship to the USA. No International shipping. I also insure all of my packages to the USA to make sure that they arrive to you safely. Any questions, please ask before purchasing. Thanks for looking. Each sign will significantly resemble one another, while having its own characteristic due to the knots, wood grain & slight variations of each piece of hand cut wood. We do not try to cover up, change, or get rid of any of these characteristics, we feel this is what makes the sign unique. We lightly distress the s to add to the rustic/ farm look & will include small imperfections which adds to the rustic character of your sign. So if you order a 50'' sign, it could be slightly longer 51" or an inch shorter 49". Name: 86916 Heavyweight Bed Mats 97 X 63 In.
Description:
Dee Zee Bed Mats are a cost-effective solution to protect your truck bed surface free from scratches, dings and dents. Shifting cargo is also a detriment to your truck's appearance. Bed Mats help prevent shifting cargo from damaging your truck and eliminate chasing down loose items strewn about the truck bed.
Dee Zee Bed Mats are custom fitting to your truck by contouring around wheel wells for ultimate coverage. Rubber cleats on the reverse side facilitate water drainage and keep the Bed Mat securely in place. you can trust heavy-duty Dee Zee Bed Mats to last the life of your truck.
Each heavy-duty Dee Zee Bed Mat is constructed from 0.375 in. (9.52mm) high-density Rubber compound that is resistant to gas or oil spills. The tightly compressed Rubber fibers are abrasion and tear resistant from your cargo. Your custom fit Bed Mat will not crack, rust or break in extreme temperatures. Resilient Rubber compound material deflects harmful UV rays to decrease fading.

Name: R12022LGPJ 5.8 ft. Painted Hard Truck Bed Cover, GPJ Glory Red Pearl for 2019-2020 GM Sierra
Description:
The ARE Fusion Tonneau Cover combines the custom look of a painted truck bed cover with the functionality of a hard folding cover. Constructed from heavy duty aluminum panels that are highly dent resistant to keep your cover looking great. ARE adds a convenient battery operated LED light along with durable carpeted paneling underneath, completing that custom look. The Fusion can be operated from either side of the truck bed by pulling the release cable to disengage the slam latches. When closing the cover, the slam latches will automatically lock the cover to the rails. A universal tailgate seal helps prevent water from seeping in while allowing you to open and close the tailgate with the cover closed. Full bed access is possible in seconds with the Fusion truck bed cover. Release the slam latches and fold the cover, panel by panel, towards the cab for partial bed access. Full bed access is achieved by lifting the cover towards the cab and attaching the support arms to securely drive down the road with the cover up. The Fusion has L-rails that mount to the bed caps with clamp-on brackets, providing a no-drill installation. For weather protection, interior and exterior seals help to keep most of the elements out. The provided drain tubes work with the mounting rails like gutters to help flush out excess water to keep your cargo dry. Drilling may be needed if your truck does not have factory drain holes.
FeaturesFits 2019-2020 GM Sierra 5 '8inches bed 1500 w / or w / out Multipro Tailgate Paint Code: GPJ Glory Red Pearl
Aluminum panels are painted-to-match your truck's color code
Exterior and interior seals help deflect elements from entering your bed and the integrated drain track helps push any water to the front and out of bed
Open your tailgate with the cover in the opened or closed position
Cover can be propped open with integrated support arms, allowing you to drive with the cover in the fully opened position
Made in the USA
Compatibility:2019-2020 GM Sierra
SpecificationsSize: 5.8'
Country of Origin: United States

Name: 86793 Heavyweight Bed Mats 97.25 X 64 In.
Description:
Dee Zee Bed Mats are a cost-effective solution to protect your truck bed surface free from scratches, dings and dents. Shifting cargo is also a detriment to your truck's appearance. Bed Mats help prevent shifting cargo from damaging your truck and eliminate chasing down loose items strewn about the truck bed.
Dee Zee Bed Mats are custom fitting to your truck by contouring around wheel wells for ultimate coverage. Rubber cleats on the reverse side facilitate water drainage and keep the Bed Mat securely in place. you can trust heavy-duty Dee Zee Bed Mats to last the life of your truck.
Each heavy-duty Dee Zee Bed Mat is constructed from 0.375 in. (9.52mm) high-density Rubber compound that is resistant to gas or oil spills. The tightly compressed Rubber fibers are abrasion and tear resistant from your cargo. Your custom fit Bed Mat will not crack, rust or break in extreme temperatures. Resilient Rubber compound material deflects harmful UV rays to decrease fading.

Helps Prevent Cargo From Shifting & Damaging Your Truck Bed

Name: Loft Style Industrial Design Handmade Iron Bed - Model Pandora | Creates A Unique Bedroom Decor
Description: Find a unique industrial handmade iron bed . Lifetime Guarantee, Eco-friendly & safe. Handmade metal beds made by Volcano, Greece. Shipping worldwide ...In industrial style to create a unique bedroom decor. It is made of wrought iron with rebar steel rods "Lifetime Guarantee" The guarantee covers the welds & the stability of the structure of the bed. Assembly time: only 15 minutes (The product accompanied by detailed instructions with images). The bed can be constructed only in 1 type: 1. Bed without Footboard (NO-FTB) All beds include Anatomic  (mattress base) with 11 wood boards, providing maximum strength & stability to the bed. It can be manufactured in any dimension & color you choose from the list above. Tip For a better aesthetic result, the bed should be in a colour contrasting the wall, to emphasize its design. The paintjobs are done with acrylic powder paints & cured in a special oven at 200c. This results in the perfect adhesion of the paint onto the metal, ensuring longer durability over time. If you choose color with patina, we inform you that it's applied exclusively to the design of the bed & not to the side parts & the base of the bed. All materials used in the production of the products are recyclable. The fabric dries quickly after washing & does not need ironing. Name: Last Name & Established Date Sign | With Quote Inspirations Signs Above Bed Decor Anniversary Gift Wedding
Description: Each sign is handmade from solid Pine wood We use Chalk paint on all of our lettering to get that vintage/farm look. We use a high quality oil based stain for our s. We use a Flat ultra white interior paint for the white background on all of our boards.Our signs are NOT made with vinyl lettering, & we DO NOT use canvas or thin material for the construction of our products. Our signs are not made by mass production, when you order a sign & it is made JUST FOR YOU. Every sign is hand painted & hand made for each individual order. Each sign will significantly resemble one another, while having its own characteristic due to the knots, wood grain & slight variations of each piece of hand cut wood. We do not try to cover up, change, or get rid of any of these characteristics, we feel this is what makes the sign unique. We lightly distress the s to add to the rustic/ farm look & will include small imperfections which adds to the rustic character of your sign. Our items are made from cut pine, & put together with wood glue & high quality nails. When ordering signs, please be aware that the size could be 1'' larger or smaller. So if you order a 50'' sign, it could be slightly longer 51" or an inch shorter 49". This happens during the inspection of our boards, we do this in the interest of our customers to ensure your getting a clean, gorgeous piece of wood. (Due to knots & imperfections) These signs are made to be used indoors, but can be placed outdoors although they will age, fade & may warp outdoors. Name: Antique Copper Bed Warmer Or Warming Pan 38 " Star On Lid
Description: This is a Antique Copper Bed Warmer or Warming Pan with a Star design on the Lid. It measures approx. 38 inches long. The handle is wood & it has been turned. There is a hole in the end of the wood handle where a little metal loop used to be so it could be hung on the wall, but it is missing. These were made from the 1500's to the late 1800's. Guess they finally figured out the putting embers in them to warm a bed up was not so safe to breathe & also caused fires. Glad we do not have to use them anymore. It is in good condition with normal age wear. I will let the buyer clean it if they want to shine the copper up...I do not like to alter antiques & collectibles. This would really look great hanging by a Fireplace for the Farm look. I ship to the USA. No International shipping. I also insure all of my packages to the USA to make sure that they arrive to you safely. Any questions, please ask before purchasing. Thanks for looking. Name: As For Me & My  We Will Serve The Lord | Living Room Sign d Signs With Quote Above Bed
Description: Each sign is handmade from solid Pine wood We use Chalk paint on all of our lettering to get that vintage/farm look. We use a high quality oil based stain for our s. We use a Flat ultra white interior paint for the white background on all of our boards.Our signs are NOT made with vinyl lettering, & we DO NOT use canvas or thin material for the construction of our products. Our signs are not made by mass production, when you order a sign & it is made JUST FOR YOU. Every sign is hand painted & hand made for each individual order. Each sign will significantly resemble one another, while having its own characteristic due to the knots, wood grain & slight variations of each piece of hand cut wood. We do not try to cover up, change, or get rid of any of these characteristics, we feel this is what makes the sign unique. We lightly distress the s to add to the rustic/ farm look & will include small imperfections which adds to the rustic character of your sign. Our items are made from cut pine, & put together with wood glue & high quality nails. When ordering signs, please be aware that the size could be 1'' larger or smaller. So if you order a 50'' sign, it could be slightly longer 51" or an inch shorter 49". This happens during the inspection of our boards, we do this in the interest of our customers to ensure your getting a clean, gorgeous piece of wood. (Due to knots & imperfections) These signs are made to be used indoors, but can be placed outdoors although they will age, fade & may warp outdoors. Name: 86973 Heavyweight Bed Mats
Description:
Bed Mats are a cost-effective solution to protect your truck bed surface free from scratches, dings and dents. Shifting cargo is also a detriment to your truck's appearance. Bed Mats help prevent shifting cargo from damaging your truck and eliminate chasing down loose items strewn about the truck bed.
Bed Mats are custom fitting to your truck by contouring around wheel wells for ultimate coverage. Rubber cleats on the reverse side facilitate water drainage and keep the Bed Mat securely in place. you can trust heavy-duty Bed Mats to last the life of your truck.
Each heavy-duty Bed Mat is constructed from 0.375 in. (9.52mm) high-density Rubber compound that is resistant to gas or oil spills. The tightly compressed Rubber fibers are abrasion and tear resistant from your cargo. Your custom fit Bed Mat will not crack, rust or break in extreme temperatures. Resilient Rubber compound material deflects harmful UV rays to decrease fading.
Features Heavyweight Bed Mat
Helps Prevent Cargo From Shifting & Damaging Your Truck Bed

Rubber Cleats Help Keep Mat In Place & Allow Water to Drain

Will Not Rust, Crack, Or Break - Even In Extreme Temperatures
Resists Common Fuel & Oil Spills
Rubber Material Deflects UV Rays To Reduce Fading

Description:
Dee Zee Bed Mats are a cost-effective solution to protect your truck bed surface free from scratches, dings and dents. Shifting cargo is also a detriment to your truck's appearance. Bed Mats help prevent shifting cargo from damaging your truck and eliminate chasing down loose items strewn about the truck bed.
Dee Zee Bed Mats are custom fitting to your truck by contouring around wheel wells for ultimate coverage. Rubber cleats on the reverse side facilitate water drainage and keep the Bed Mat securely in place. you can trust heavy-duty Dee Zee Bed Mats to last the life of your truck.
Each heavy-duty Dee Zee Bed Mat is constructed from 0.375 in. (9.52mm) high-density Rubber compound that is resistant to gas or oil spills. The tightly compressed Rubber fibers are abrasion and tear resistant from your cargo. Your custom fit Bed Mat will not crack, rust or break in extreme temperatures. Resilient Rubber compound material deflects harmful UV rays to decrease fading.

Name: R12022LGPJ 5.8 ft. Painted Hard Truck Bed Cover, GPJ Glory Red Pearl for 2019-2020 GM Sierra
Description:
The ARE Fusion Tonneau Cover combines the custom look of a painted truck bed cover with the functionality of a hard folding cover. Constructed from heavy duty aluminum panels that are highly dent resistant to keep your cover looking great. ARE adds a convenient battery operated LED light along with durable carpeted paneling underneath, completing that custom look. The Fusion can be operated from either side of the truck bed by pulling the release cable to disengage the slam latches. When closing the cover, the slam latches will automatically lock the cover to the rails. A universal tailgate seal helps prevent water from seeping in while allowing you to open and close the tailgate with the cover closed. Full bed access is possible in seconds with the Fusion truck bed cover. Release the slam latches and fold the cover, panel by panel, towards the cab for partial bed access. Full bed access is achieved by lifting the cover towards the cab and attaching the support arms to securely drive down the road with the cover up. The Fusion has L-rails that mount to the bed caps with clamp-on brackets, providing a no-drill installation. For weather protection, interior and exterior seals help to keep most of the elements out. The provided drain tubes work with the mounting rails like gutters to help flush out excess water to keep your cargo dry. Drilling may be needed if your truck does not have factory drain holes.
FeaturesFits 2019-2020 GM Sierra 5 '8inches bed 1500 w / or w / out Multipro Tailgate Paint Code: GPJ Glory Red Pearl
Aluminum panels are painted-to-match your truck's color code
Exterior and interior seals help deflect elements from entering your bed and the integrated drain track helps push any water to the front and out of bed
Open your tailgate with the cover in the opened or closed position
Cover can be propped open with integrated support arms, allowing you to drive with the cover in the fully opened position
Made in the USA
Compatibility:2019-2020 GM Sierra
SpecificationsSize: 5.8'
Country of Origin: United States
